{"tid":404943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我呀媽執咗張凳，依家點算好","createTime":"2017-09-18T13:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T01:56:01.000Z","uid":138209,"like":133,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"064d734cfbf05a936d13d824b6380a3e409cdd52","tid":404943,"uid":138209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"頭先呀媽出去揼垃圾，結果返嚟多咗張人地唔要嘅凳，係隔離屋揼，我係咁叫佢唔好要都唔聽，仲要鬧返我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢解釋張凳可能好污穢，加上呢幾日睇到好多post話屋企有蝨有蟲，搞到自己都驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但佢一味話張凳好靚架，我消毒下佢咪無事囉，死都唔肯攞返出去。講真，人地唔要張凳都証明可能有問題，仲要執佢返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家都唔知點算好，同佢講道理又話我駁嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲有相似經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e7a5ba35a15b2b37ac3ff0239672dbb5512ef9","tid":404943,"uid":128413,"like":25,"dislike":41,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"登登燈櫈！"},{"pid":"7b6bf242a86ba1dc562a7d4aa6c28fa9789c29e2","tid":404943,"uid":73909,"like":155,"dislike":2,"score":153,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:04:12.000Z","msg":"整到佢變霍金"},{"pid":"104a4b420fbb70e509e281e5ad93b122eb8f32c2","tid":404943,"uid":138252,"like":62,"dislike":13,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"有尐on9既老母真係命都少幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07453f5348694b236d4217bd39bb638590f30bdc","tid":404943,"uid":138209,"like":7,"dislike":81,"score":-74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整到佢變霍金</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢平時待我不薄"},{"pid":"7b25b4435e9ab1b58f6732c560c43cf7dcc8be63","tid":404943,"uid":43483,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:07:58.000Z","msg":"直接拎落樓下垃圾站啦<br />\n講係無用行動最實際"},{"pid":"7af83c64355e0fc9df39adc6112